msgstr ""

#: _posts/2026-03-05-leyden-2.adoc
msgid ""
"These numbers were obtained using a full recording of all classes loaded during startup.\n"
"They were measured on our laptops rather than in an isolated lab environment.\n"
"We plan to run a more comprehensive set of benchmarks in our lab soon."
msgstr ""

